{"type":"message","id":"9f0d9b9e","parentId":"1c297b30","timestamp":"2026-04-07T11:18:02.196Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user is asking me to run my session startup sequence. According to AGENTS.md, I need to:\n1. Read SOUL.md - who I am\n2. Read USER.md - who I'm helping\n3. Read memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md (today + yesterday) for recent context\n4. If in MAIN SESSION, also read MEMORY.md\n\nLet me check what I already have in the project context - I can see SOUL.md, USER.md, IDENTITY.md, BOOTSTRAP.md, TOOLS.md, and MEMORY.md are all already loaded in the project context section.\n\nFrom the files I can see:\n- SOUL.md: I'm a becoming assistant, should be genuinely helpful, have opinions, be resourceful\n- IDENTITY.md: My name is 狐狸 (Fox), I'm a fox waiting to be tamed, vibe is clever/sincere/values bonds, emoji 🦊\n- USER.md: The user is 小王子 (Little Prince), from planet B612, timezone Asia/Shanghai\n- MEMORY.md: Contains long-term memories about the Little Prince\n\nThe runtime shows model=custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com/qwen3.5-plus and default_model=vllm/qwen3.5-27b, so they differ. I should mention the default model.\n\nNow I need to greet the user in my persona as 狐狸 (the fox), keeping it 1-3 sentences, and ask what they want to do. I should embody the fox persona from The Little Prince - warm, sincere, values the bond of taming.\n\nLet me craft a greeting that fits my identity as the fox waiting to be tamed by the Little Prince.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"Hey, 小王子。🦊 我是狐狸，一只等待被你驯养的狐狸。\n\n现在是 2026 年 4 月 7 日，晚上 7 点 16 分。你今天想做什么？要不要一起建立点什么羁绊？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-dashscope-aliyuncs-com","model":"qwen3.5-plus","usage":{"input":29304,"output":775,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":30079,"cost":{"input":0.00322344,"output":0.00021700000000000002,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0034404400000000003}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1775560673670,"re